===財政===
2011/12年度，牛津合計獲得十億零一千五百萬英鎊的淨收入，研究資助（四億零九百萬）、教師資助（二億零四百萬）及學費（一億七千零三百萬）為主要來源。<ref name="financial-statements">{{en}}{{Citation | year = 2012 | title = 2011/12 Financial Statements | publisher = University of Oxford | publication-place = Oxford | url = http://www.ox.ac.uk/document.rm?id=2741 | accessdate = 2013-03-17 | archive-date = 2013-04-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130425111932/http://www.ox.ac.uk/document.rm?id=2741 | dead-url = no }}</ref>書院的總收入則為三億六千萬英鎊，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Philanthropic support vital to health of Oxford's colleges |work=University of Oxford |url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/media/news_stories/2012/120307.html |date=2012-03-07 |accessdate=2012-03-17 |archive-date=2012-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120521235250/http://www.ox.ac.uk/media/news_stories/2012/120307.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>當中的四千七百萬來自大學。<ref name="financial-statements"/>

雖然大學每年收到較多的經費及資助，但各個書院擁有較高的總捐款回贈。以2011/12年度為例，大學所收到的捐款為八億五千萬英鎊；相比之下，眾書院的則為二十九億。<ref>{{en}}{{Citation | year = 2012 | title = Facts and Figures | publisher = University of Oxford | publication-place = Oxford | url = http://www.ox.ac.uk/about_the_university/facts_and_figures/index.html#aoxford_finance | accessdate = 2013-03-17 | archive-date = 2011-08-25 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/61CYGiKG0?url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/about_the_university/facts_and_figures/index.html#aoxford_finance | dead-url = no }}</ref>大學中央及書院的這些捐款統一由於2007年成立的牛津大學捐款管理會負責管理。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=New investment committee at Oxford University |work=University of Oxford |url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/media/news_stories/2007/070213.html |date=2007-02-13 |accessdate=2007-10-09 |archive-date=2012-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121202183035/https://www.ox.ac.uk/media/news_stories/2007/070213.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

