===錄取===
與其他英國大學一樣，牛津大學透過[[UCAS|UCAS]]系統招收本科生。特別注意的是報考牛津、劍橋及其他大學的醫學、牙醫及獸醫課程的學生，需提早於每年的10月15號前完成系統登記的手續。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=UCAS Students: Important dates for your diary |quote=15 October 2009 Last date for receipt of applications to Oxford University, University of Cambridge and courses in medicine, dentistry and veterinary science or veterinary medicine. |url=http://www.ucas.com/students/importantdates |accessdate=2009-11-23 |archive-date=2009-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201114118/http://ucas.com/students/importantdates |dead-url=no }}</ref>另外，為了能有更好的個性化判斷，學生不能同時報考牛津及劍橋（報讀第二個本科課程的申請者例外）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.williamfarr.lincs.sch.uk/care-and-guidance/university-applications/oxford-and-cambridge-application|quote=You cannot apply to both Oxford and Cambridge in the same year.|title=Oxford and Cambridge Application|publisher=William Farr School|accessdate=2014-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218045849/http://www.williamfarr.lincs.sch.uk/care-and-guidance/university-applications/oxford-and-cambridge-application|archive-date=2015-02-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>大多的學生都選擇申請其中一所書院，而書院之間也會互相交流，確保合資格的學生能找到最適合自己的書院，亦不會因為對某一書院的偏好而不獲錄取。

優先考慮的原則包括預期的公開考試結果、各類的推薦信以及即時的入學考試（適用於某些學系）及面試的成績。每年大約有60%的申請者夠資格獲得優先考慮。若太多獲優先考慮的申請者傾向於同一所書院，則這些學生會被重新分配至收生不足的書院，有關書院亦會為這些學生安排面試，面試輪候期間，受邀的學生會獲得3天的免費食宿。一名學生可獲多所書院安排面試。居住在歐洲以外的學生可透過互聯網進行面試評核。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=How do I choose a college? – Will I be interviewed only at my chosen college?|url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/admissions/undergraduate_courses/colleges/how_do_i_choose_a_college/index.html|publisher=University of Oxford|accessdate=2009-11-23|archive-date=2010-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100110064825/http://www.ox.ac.uk/admissions/undergraduate_courses/colleges/how_do_i_choose_a_college/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

錄取通知通常在聖誕節前夕、由書院寄出（2012-13學年的錄取則延遲至1月）。每年大約有四分之一獲錄取的學生進入自己沒有申請的書院。某些大學課程採用開放式錄取，允許在8月高級程度考試（高考）放榜後，重新審視先前未獲任何一所書院錄取的學生。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Open Offer Scheme |url=http://www.bioch.ox.ac.uk/aspsite/index.asp?pageid=462 |publisher=Department of Biochemistry, University of Oxford |accessdate=2009-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606054422/http://www.bioch.ox.ac.uk/aspsite/index.asp?pageid=462 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Open Offer Scheme |url=http://www2.physics.ox.ac.uk/study-here/undergraduates/faqs/faq-admissions |publisher=Department of Physics, University of Oxford |accessdate=2013-03-27 |archive-date=2013-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707214158/http://www2.physics.ox.ac.uk/study-here/undergraduates/faqs/faq-admissions |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

===教學===
牛津的本科課程包括每週的書院輔導，及学部提供的各學科課程。大約1-4名學生會被分為一組，每週與由書院提供的導師一起商討學習進度，及所面對的困難。授課形式主要為論文表達（適用於大多數修讀人文及社會科學的學生；亦包括部分數學及物理科學的學生）或解難能力測試（適用於大多數的數理生及部分社會科學學生）。牛津的本科教育每年分為三個[[學期|學期]]——[[米迦勒學期|米迦勒學期]]、[[希拉里學期|希拉里學期]]及[[復活節學期|復活節學期]]，每個學期為時八週，比其他大多數英國大學的短。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | title=Regulations on the number and length of terms | work=University of Oxford | url=http://www.admin.ox.ac.uk/examregs/03-00_REGULATIONS_ON_THE_NUMBER_AND_LENGTH_OF_TERMS.shtml | accessdate=2007-10-09 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527150600/http://www.admin.ox.ac.uk/examregs/03-00_REGULATIONS_ON_THE_NUMBER_AND_LENGTH_OF_TERMS.shtml | archivedate=2008-05-27 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>

大學所有的學系均有提供研究生課程，課程主要由有關学部提供。

===獎學金與資助===
牛津大學提供不同的學生資助及獎學金。牛津大學助學金計劃於2006年創立，為所有的大學3年本科生提供高達10,235英鎊的資助，金額為全英之冠。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Oxford Opportunity Bursaries |work=University of Oxford |url=http://www.oxfordopportunity.com/ |accessdate=2007-10-09 |archive-date=2007-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071013041136/http://www.oxfordopportunity.com/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>各書院同時也有不同種類的基金，幫助有需要的學生。牛津亦為多個研究生獎學金計劃的基地，如[[羅德獎學金|羅德獎學金]]、韋登菲爾德獎學金<ref>{{en}}{{Cite news |title=Oxford targets bright young things of eastern Europe |work=The Guardian |location=UK |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/education/2007/mar/22/highereducation.internationaleducationnews |date=2007-03-22 |accessdate=2007-10-09 |first=Jessica |last=Shepherd |archive-date=2008-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207085627/http://www.guardian.co.uk/education/2007/mar/22/highereducation.internationaleducationnews |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[克拉倫登獎學金|克拉倫登獎學金]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.clarendon.ox.ac.uk/informationforapplicants/eligibility/ |title=Eligibility criteria, Clarendon Fund Scholarships |publisher=Clarendon.ox.ac.uk |date= |accessdate=2014-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413150702/http://www.clarendon.ox.ac.uk/informationforapplicants/eligibility/ |archive-date=2014-04-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.clarendon.ox.ac.uk/about/history/ |title=History of the Clarendon Fund, Clarendon Fund Scholarships |publisher=Clarendon.ox.ac.uk |date=2011-09-01 |accessdate=2014-04-11 |archive-date=2014-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413150925/http://www.clarendon.ox.ac.uk/about/history/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.clarendon.ox.ac.uk/about/partnership/ |title=Partnership awards, Clarendon Fund Scholarships |publisher=Clarendon.ox.ac.uk |date= |accessdate=2014-04-11 |archive-date=2014-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413150734/http://www.clarendon.ox.ac.uk/about/partnership/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

=== 圖書館及博物館 ===
另見：[[:Category:牛津大學圖書館|:Category:牛津大學圖書館]]及[[:Category:牛津大學博物館|:Category:牛津大學博物館]]

牛津大學擁有全英最大型的[[大學圖書館|大學圖書館]]系統，系統包含100所圖書館，館藏量合計逾1100萬冊，<ref name=uls/>此數字仍在不斷增長。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=A University Library for the Twenty-first Century |work=University of Oxford |url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/gazette/2005-6/supps/1_4743.htm |date=2005-09-22 |accessdate=2007-10-09 |archive-date=2007-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070902222824/http://www.ox.ac.uk/gazette/2005-6/supps/1_4743.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>當中的[[博德利圖書館|博德利圖書館]]為[[法定送存|法定送存]]地，亦是全英國第二大的圖書館（僅次於[[大英圖書館|大英圖書館]]）。這所大學最主要的研究圖書館的建築還包括舊校區的方庭，此方庭是由{{link-en|托馬斯·博德利|Thomas Bodley}}於1598年建立，後在1602年正式啟用。

大學於2000年正式將博德利與個別的學科圖書館組合成[[博德利圖書館群|博德利圖書館群]]<ref name="timeline">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/__data/assets/pdf_file/0003/113853/BodLibs-TIMELINE-2000-2012.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121123105538/http://www.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/__data/assets/pdf_file/0003/113853/BodLibs-TIMELINE-2000-2012.pdf|format=PDF|title=Timeline of Bodleian Libraries Events from 2000|accessdate=2012-12-16|archive-date=2012-11-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，此群組現包含28所圖書館（成員包括[[賽克勒圖書館|賽克勒圖書館]]、{{link-en|牛津大學社會科學圖書館|Social Science Library, Oxford|社會科學圖書館}}及{{link-en|拉德克利夫科學圖書館|Radcliffe Science Library}}等）。<ref name="Bodleian_Libraries_list">{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/libraries/libraries/bodleian | title = Bodleian Libraries | publisher = Bodleian Library | archivedate = 2012-12-16 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6CxhhPZtR?url=http://www.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/libraries/libraries/bodleian | accessdate = 2011-11-17 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref name="timeline"/>此聯誼亦創立{{link-en|牛津大學圖書館信息系統|Oxford Libraries Information System}}（{{lang|en|OLIS}}）,<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/bdlss/olis-ils |title=Bodleian Digital Library Systems and Services | OLIS (Integrated Library System) |publisher=Bodleian.ox.ac.uk |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archive-date=2013-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827200924/http://www.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/bdlss/olis-ils |dead-url=no }}</ref>及其對外開放的“牛津圖書館線上搜尋系統”（{{lang|en|SOLO}}，內含大學各個圖書館的目錄表）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://libguides.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/solo|title=Contents - SOLO - Search Oxford Libraries Online|publisher=Bodleian Libraries, University of Oxford|accessdate=2014-06-04|archive-date=2013-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618121121/http://libguides.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/solo|dead-url=no}}</ref>博德利亦與[[谷歌|谷歌]]在2004年間合作，進行大規模的數字化系統更新項目。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | title = Oxford-Google Digitization Programme | work = Bodleian Library | url = http://www.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/dbooks | accessdate = 2007-10-09 | archive-date = 2011-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111129044607/http://www.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/dbooks/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web | title = Library Partners | publisher = Google | url = http://www.google.co.uk/intl/en/googlebooks/library/partners.html | accessdate = 2007-10-09 | archive-date = 2013-12-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131228214111/http://www.google.co.uk/intl/en/googlebooks/library/partners.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

校方亦於2010年在[[斯溫頓|斯溫頓]]的{{link-en|南馬斯頓|South Marston}}創辦一家藏書庫，<ref>{{en}}{{Cite news |title = Swindon's £26m Bodleian book store opens |work = BBC News |url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/wiltshire/hi/people_and_places/arts_and_culture/newsid_9062000/9062875.stm |date = 2010-10-06 |accessdate = 2011-09-10 |archive-date = 2012-05-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120520041325/http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/wiltshire/hi/people_and_places/arts_and_culture/newsid_9062000/9062875.stm |dead-url = no }}</ref>並計劃重塑將會於2014-15年以“韋斯頓圖書館”之名開放的新博德利建築物。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | title = New Bodleian: The Weston Library | work = University of Oxford | url = http://www.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/news/2009_mar_13 | date = 2009-03-13 | accessdate = 2013-03-27 | archive-date = 2013-03-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130323144008/http://www.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/news/2009_mar_13 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

牛津同時開辦多所藝術及博物館。其中，於1683年創立的[[阿什莫林博物館|阿什莫林博物館]]是全英最古老的博物館，亦為全球歷史最悠久的大學博物館。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Support Us |work=The Ashmolean |url=http://www.ashmolean.org/support/corporatesupport/about/ |accessdate=2007-10-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070503032502/http://www.ashmolean.org/support/corporatesupport/about/ |archivedate=2007-05-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>館內有多個藝術及考古學收藏，包括[[米開朗基羅|米開朗基羅]]，[[達芬奇|達芬奇]]，[[特納|特納]]和[[畢加索|畢加索]]的作品。大學的[[牛津大學自然史博物館|自然史博物館]]在位於{{link-en|公園道|Parks Road}}的{{link-en|牛津大學科學區|Science Area, Oxford|科學區}}內，採用新哥特式建築風格打造，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.oum.ox.ac.uk/|title=Oxford University Museum of Natural History Homepage|publisher=[[Oxford_University_Museum_of_Natural_History|Oxford University Museum of Natural History]]|accessdate=2007-11-04|archive-date=2007-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071027090448/http://www.oum.ox.ac.uk/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/visitors_friends/maps_and_directions/#qmuseums_libraries_and_places_of_interest|title=Map of Museums, Libraries and Places of Interest|year=2006|publisher=University of Oxford|accessdate=2007-11-04|archive-date=2007-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071027080434/http://www.ox.ac.uk/visitors_friends/maps_and_directions/#qmuseums_libraries_and_places_of_interest|dead-url=no}}</ref>內藏多個[[動物學|動物學]]，[[昆蟲學|昆蟲學]]和[[地質|地質]]標本，包括一副[[霸王龍|霸王龍]]及[[三角龍|三角龍]]的骸骨，及[[渡渡鳥|渡渡鳥]]的殘骸。毗鄰自然史博物館的，是於1884年成立的[[皮特·里弗斯博物館|皮特·里弗斯博物館]]，內展大學的考古和[[人類學|人類學]]收藏品。自創立以來，館內的教職員都有參與校方的人類學教學工作。大學的{{link-en|牛津大學科學史博物館|Museum of the History of Science, Oxford|科學史博物館}}則坐落在[[寬街_(牛津)|寬街]]的一座世上最古老的專門性博物館建築大樓內，內收集約15000個文物。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=About the Museum |work=Museum of the History of Science |url=http://www.mhs.ox.ac.uk/about/index.htm?text |accessdate=2007-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070911135646/http://www.mhs.ox.ac.uk/about/index.htm?text |archivedate=2007-09-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>大學各博物藝術館為學生提供多元化的學習環境。

